{% style %}
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');
{% endstyle %}

<div class="plekify-v6">

<!-- SHOPIFY PLATFORM -->
<section id="platform" class="section">
  <span class="annot">Why the platform choice is a business decision</span>
  <h2 class="sh">Most travel brands are building<br><em>on the wrong foundation.</em></h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top:.65rem;margin-bottom:2.25rem">WordPress and custom sites display a property. They do not compound. Shopify is the infrastructure layer that turns a travel website into a revenue engine — with native commerce intelligence, AI-era discoverability, and an ecosystem that grows with the business. The AI pipeline designs the journey. Shopify is where it gets sold.</p>

  <table class="comp-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Capability</th><th>Shopify via Plekify</th><th>WordPress + booking plugin</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Checkout ownership</td><td class="g">100% on your domain. PCI DSS Level 1. 99.99% uptime (Plus).</td><td class="d">Typically redirects to a third-party engine to complete</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Guest data & CRM</td><td class="g">Every booking builds a Shopify customer profile — owned, segmentable, marketable</td><td class="d">Records split across PMS, plugin, and gateway — rarely unified</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Remarketing</td><td class="g">Shopify Email, abandoned checkout recovery, dynamic segments, Flow automations — all native</td><td class="d">External CRM required; PMS data rarely flows to email tools without custom dev</td></tr>
      <tr><td>AI discoverability</td><td class="g">Shopify Catalog MCP — inventory queryable by ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI agents</td><td class="d">No structured agentic discovery layer; invisible to AI shopping assistants</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Agentic commerce</td><td class="g">Universal Commerce Protocol (UCP) compliant — supports AI-led booking flows end to end</td><td class="d">No equivalent; dependent on OTAs to mediate AI-era discovery</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Payment flexibility</td><td class="g">Deposits, instalments, milestone billing, B2B terms, 130+ currencies, Shop Pay</td><td class="d">Plugin-dependent; typically single-payment flows only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>International selling</td><td class="g">Shopify Markets — localised pricing, 20+ languages, 130+ currencies, hreflang natively</td><td class="d">Plugin-dependent; hreflang and structured data require developer work</td></tr>
      <tr><td>SEO</td><td class="g">Itineraries rank on your domain — full HTML, automatic sitemaps, structured data</td><td class="d">Wetu itineraries on wetu.com; none of the SEO value flows to the operator's site</td></tr>
      <tr><td>B2B & trade channel</td><td class="g">Shopify Plus: company accounts, agent catalogues, negotiated pricing, payment terms</td><td class="d">Separate systems required; no native B2B commerce layer</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Ecosystem</td><td class="g">16 000+ managed apps — no version conflicts, no security patches, no broken upgrades</td><td class="d">Plugin stacks accumulate compatibility risk with every addition and update</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="hl-box" style="margin-top:1.75rem">
    <p class="body" style="color:#555"><strong style="font-weight:400;color:#333">The AI distribution argument:</strong> OTAs dominate AI-assistant discovery today because they hold structured, queryable inventory. Shopify Catalog MCP and the Universal Commerce Protocol give independent operators the same discoverability — without the commission, and without ceding the customer relationship. The path from a natural-language travel query to a completed booking is becoming automated. Operators on Shopify are in that flow. Operators on custom sites are not.</p>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- DIRECT CHANNEL -->
<section class="section">
  <span class="annot">The long-term case</span>
  <div class="two-col">
    <div>
      <h2 class="sh">The direct channel is the<br><em>most profitable one you own.</em></h2>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top:.75rem;margin-bottom:.85rem">Booking.com and Airbnb are traffic sources, not competitors. Properties that underinvest in their own website because it generates little direct business have confused cause with effect. The direct channel is underdeveloped because the technology has never matched what OTAs deliver. Plekify changes that equation without removing a single OTA booking or disrupting existing channel management.</p>
      <p class="body">The direct channel is the only one that simultaneously offers full margin, owned guest data, a controlled brand experience, and the compounding returns of a real CRM. No property management system, however capable, can offer all four.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="annot" style="margin-top:.1rem">What compounds with every direct booking</span>
      <div class="acc-row" style="padding-top:0"><span class="acc-title">Guest profiles build — email, stay history, spend, preferences</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
      <div class="acc-row"><span class="acc-title">Remarketing becomes possible — seasonal offers, loyalty, return stays</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
      <div class="acc-row"><span class="acc-title">Abandoned booking recovery — automated, no third-party tool required</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
      <div class="acc-row"><span class="acc-title">B2B agent channel — trade pricing and catalogues on one platform</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
      <div class="acc-row"><span class="acc-title">AI discoverability — inventory visible to agents, not just search crawlers</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
      <div class="acc-row"><span class="acc-title">Platform grows with the business — 16 000+ apps, no replatforming ever</span><span class="acc-plus">+</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- INTEGRATIONS -->
<section class="section">
  <span class="annot">Connected systems</span>
  <h2 class="sh">Existing operations.<br><em>Connected, not replaced.</em></h2>
  <p class="body" style="margin-top:.5rem;max-width:580px">Plekify does not ask operators to migrate data or change how their business runs. It connects to systems already in use and adds what those systems cannot provide: an AI design layer and a direct commerce layer on the operator's own domain.</p>
  <div class="int-grid">
    <div class="int-card">
      <span class="int-status live">Live</span>
      <div class="int-name">Wetu</div>
      <p class="body">Full property, room, activity, restaurant, spa, and itinerary synchronisation. PinID and UUID sync paths. Round-trip capability — AI pipeline designs or enhances, uploads back to Wetu, then syncs to Shopify as products, collections, and metaobjects.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="int-card">
      <span class="int-status live">Live</span>
      <div class="int-name">ResRequest</div>
      <p class="body">Live availability checks, real-time pricing, provisional reservations, and booking confirmation on payment. 400+ properties across 14 African countries.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="int-card">
      <span class="int-status soon">Roadmap</span>
      <div class="int-name">PMS integrations</div>
      <p class="body">The accommodation booking architecture connects to any PMS with an open API. NightsBridge — the dominant platform in South Africa — and Tourplan are among the systems on the integration roadmap. Additional platforms follow demand.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- THE BUILDER -->
<section id="builder" class="section">
  <span class="annot">The builder</span>
  <div class="builder-section">
    <div>
      <div class="builder-profile">
        <img class="builder-avatar" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0582/6776/2747/files/matthew-swart.jpg?v=1773736621" alt="Matthew Swart" loading="lazy">
        <div>
          <div class="builder-profile-name">Matthew Swart</div>
          <div class="builder-profile-role">Founder, Plekify</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="sh">25 years building<br><em>African travel technology.</em></h2>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top:.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem">Plekify is built by Matthew Swart. In 1999 he co-founded SafariNow.com — which grew over 18 years to R320 million in annual booking value, 150 employees, three funding rounds, and a 2017 exit to TravelStart. The problems Plekify solves are the ones that emerged from two and a half decades of operating inside the industry.</p>
      <p class="body">Plekify is available by custom arrangement. There is no self-serve install — every implementation is set up directly with Matthew to ensure the integration fits the operator's existing systems and commercial model.</p>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top:.85rem"><a class="safariNow-link" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20260109235108/https://www.safarinow.com/cms/matthew-swart" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read Matthew's SafariNow journey ↗</a></p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="annot">Selected background</span>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>1999</strong> — Co-founded SafariNow.com</div>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>18 years</strong> as CEO of SafariNow</div>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>R320m</strong> annual booking value at exit</div>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>150</strong> employees · 3 funding rounds</div>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>2017</strong> — Sold to TravelStart</div>
      <div class="builder-stat"><strong>25 years</strong> building African travel technology</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- PRICING -->
<section class="section">
  <span class="annot">Two ways to start</span>
  <h2 class="sh">Choose the model that<br><em>fits how you operate.</em></h2>
  <div class="price-grid">
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-type">SaaS model</div>
      <div class="price-name">Your store, our engine</div>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top:.5rem">Plekify is installed on your Shopify store. Your brand, your domain, your customer data. Implementation fee plus monthly subscription. Full control and first-party data ownership from day one.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="price-card featured">
      <div class="price-type">Commission model</div>
      <div class="price-name">Zero upfront cost</div>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top:.5rem">Plekify builds and operates the store. You provide the content and fulfil the bookings. Commission on completed transactions only — no implementation fee, no monthly cost. For operators who want to test without commitment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<div id="contact" class="cta-section">
  <span class="eyebrow">Custom distribution · Get in touch</span>
  <h2 class="sh" style="margin-top:.75rem">Connect your existing operations.<br><em>Nothing needs to change to begin.</em></h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin:1rem auto 0;text-align:center;font-size:13.5px;max-width:480px">Existing Wetu content, PMS connections, and OTA channels continue without disruption. The AI design pipeline and a direct commerce layer are added to what is already there.</p>
  <div>
    <a class="cta-btn" href="mailto:matt@plekify.com">Talk to Matthew ↗</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="plekify-v6-footer">
  <div class="footer-logo">Plekify</div>
  <div class="footer-note">AI itinerary design · Travel commerce · Built on Shopify</div>
</footer>

</div>

{% stylesheet %}
.plekify-v6 {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  background: #fff;
  max-width: 940px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
}
.plekify-v6 h2.sh {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3.2vw, 38px);
  line-height: 1.12;
  color: #111;
  margin-bottom: .5rem;
}
.plekify-v6 h2.sh em { font-style: italic; color: #666; }
.plekify-v6 .eyebrow {
  font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #aaa; font-weight: 400;
}
.plekify-v6 p.lead {
  font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; font-weight: 300; max-width: 620px;
}
.plekify-v6 p.body { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.85; color: #555; font-weight: 300; }
.plekify-v6 .annot {
  font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: .6rem; display: block;
}
.plekify-v6 .section { margin: 2.5rem 0; }
.plekify-v6 .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
.plekify-v6 .hl-box {
  background: #f7f7f7; border-left: 2px solid #ccc; padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem; margin-top: 1.1rem;
}
/* COMP TABLE */
.plekify-v6 .comp-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
.plekify-v6 .comp-table th {
  font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #888; font-weight: 400; padding: .5rem .75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}
.plekify-v6 .comp-table td {
  padding: .6rem .75rem; color: #555; border-bottom: .5px solid #eee; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55; font-weight: 300;
}
.plekify-v6 .comp-table td:first-child { color: #333; font-weight: 400; width: 28%; }
.plekify-v6 .comp-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.plekify-v6 .comp-table td.g { color: #333; }
.plekify-v6 .comp-table td.d { color: #999; }
/* ACC ROWS */
.plekify-v6 .acc-row {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding: .8rem 0; border-bottom: .5px solid #eee;
}
.plekify-v6 .acc-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.plekify-v6 .acc-title { font-size: 13px; color: #333; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: .01em; line-height: 1.5; }
.plekify-v6 .acc-plus { font-size: 14px; color: #bbb; font-weight: 300; }
/* INTEGRATIONS */
.plekify-v6 .int-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.plekify-v6 .int-card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 1px; padding: 1.25rem; }
.plekify-v6 .int-status {
  font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .65rem; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 1px; display: inline-block;
}
.plekify-v6 .int-status.live { color: #2d6b36; background: #e8f2ea; border: 1px solid #b6d4bb; }
.plekify-v6 .int-status.soon { color: #666; background: #f0f0f0; border: 1px solid #d4d4d4; }
.plekify-v6 .int-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 300; color: #111; margin-bottom: .35rem; }
/* BUILDER */
.plekify-v6 .builder-section { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.plekify-v6 .builder-stat {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: #666; padding: .5rem 0; border-bottom: .5px solid #e8e8e8; line-height: 1.5;
}
.plekify-v6 .builder-stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.plekify-v6 .builder-stat strong { font-weight: 400; color: #222; }
.plekify-v6 .builder-profile { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.plekify-v6 .builder-avatar {
  width: 96px; height: 96px; border-radius: 1px; object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; border: 1px solid #d8d8d8; flex-shrink: 0; filter: grayscale(20%);
}
.plekify-v6 .builder-profile-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 300; color: #111; line-height: 1.2; }
.plekify-v6 .builder-profile-role { font-size: 10.5px; color: #888; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-top: 2px; }
.plekify-v6 .safariNow-link {
  font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: .06em; color: #555; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: 1px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 400; transition: color .18s, border-color .18s;
}
.plekify-v6 .safariNow-link:hover { color: #111; border-color: #888; }
/* PRICING */
.plekify-v6 .price-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.plekify-v6 .price-card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 1px; padding: 1.5rem; }
.plekify-v6 .price-card.featured { border: 1px solid #999; }
.plekify-v6 .price-type { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #888; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
.plekify-v6 .price-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; color: #111; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
/* CTA */
.plekify-v6 .cta-section {
  text-align: center; padding: 3rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 2.5rem 0;
}
.plekify-v6 .cta-btn {
  font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff; background: #111; padding: 12px 28px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 1px; border: none; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; margin-top: 1.5rem; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
}
/* FOOTER */
.plekify-v6 .plekify-v6-footer {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 2rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}
.plekify-v6 .footer-logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: #999; letter-spacing: .06em; }
.plekify-v6 .footer-note { font-size: 11px; color: #999; letter-spacing: .04em; }

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .plekify-v6 .two-col,
  .plekify-v6 .int-grid,
  .plekify-v6 .price-grid,
  .plekify-v6 .builder-section {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .plekify-v6 .plekify-v6-footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; }
}
{% endstylesheet %}

